/* Since the test statistic of 1.2638 casual rentals is less than two, we conclude the variances 
	for Holiday and Non-Holiday are equal enough. 
	
	The test that is appropriate to assess the distributions of two observations obtained between 
	two separate groups is the Wilcoxon Rank Sum Test.*/

